#CHIP YM2608
#CLOCK 7987200

; YM2608 (OPNA) ADPCM Channels Test
;
; The YM2608 includes two ADPCM sample playback channels:
; - ADPCM-A: 6 channels of high-quality sample playback
; - ADPCM-B: 1 channel of drum sample playback
;
; Tests ADPCM functionality:
; - Sample start address
; - Pitch/frequency control
; - Envelope (volume sweep)

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; ADPCM-A: Play sample at varying pitches
; Note: Actual sample data would be required in production
; This test validates register writes and timing

; ADPCM-B: Drum sample (single drum hit)
; Expected: crisp attack, natural decay

; Simple note sequence to validate ADPCM register timing
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r2

#END
